<title>UK: Credit Suisse sets warrants on silver.</title>
<headline>Credit Suisse sets warrants on silver.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-08-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Suisse says it has issued 30 million American-style call warrants, in two equal tranches, on silver.</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 09.SEP.96-27.AUG.97   PAYDATE	06.SEP.96</p>
<p> LISTING	   NONE			MIN EXER LOT 1000</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  $5.28 PER OUNCE</p>
<p> WARRANTS	STRIKE     ISS PRICE     PREMIUM     GEARING</p>
<p> CALL A	  $5.50	$0.48	   13.20 PCT   11.0 TIMES</p>
<p> CALL B	  $6.00	$0.30	   19.30 PCT   17.6 TIMES</p>
<p> NOTES	     </p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
